I"™<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Demand_forecasting">Demand forecasting</a> can be described as the use of predictive analytics to determine the <strong>expected demand</strong> for products or services. It is mostly applied in industries with <strong>volatile products</strong>, and has the potential to minimise or even completely <strong>eliminate losses</strong> resulting from spoilt items.</p>
